on><![CDATA[<section class="css-1ugvd2u e1y6i3a60"><style data-emotion="css j1vyw6">.css-j1vyw6 img{display:block;}.css-j1vyw6 .e16qazw92{margin-top:0.25rem;}</style><figure class="css-j1vyw6 e12yhaj20"><img alt="VinFast VF e35 电动汽车将于 2021 年在洛杉矶亮相" fetchpriority="high" width="1280" height="720" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" style="color:transparent" sizes="(min-width: 960px) 700px, 95vw" srcset="https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=360,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230819_WBP507.jpg 360w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=384,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230819_WBP507.jpg 384w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=480,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230819_WBP507.jpg 480w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=600,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230819_WBP507.jpg 600w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=834,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230819_WBP507.jpg 834w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=960,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230819_WBP507.jpg 960w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=1096,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230819_WBP507.jpg 1096w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=1280,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230819_WBP507.jpg 1280w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=1424,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230819_WBP507.jpg 1424w" src="https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=1424,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230819_WBP507.jpg" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"><style data-emotion="css 18w36g1">.css-18w36g1{width:100%;font-family:var(--ds-type-system-sans);}</style><figcaption class="css-18w36g1 e16qazw92"><style data-emotion="css 11jvxbd">.css-11jvxbd{font-family:var(--ds-type-system-sans-smallcaps);font-size:var(--ds-type-scale--1);font-weight:400;font-variant-ligatures:none;line-height:var(--ds-type-leading-lower);text-transform:lowercase;color:var(--ds-color-london-35);}.e16qazw90+.css-11jvxbd{margin-left:0.5rem;}</style><span class="css-11jvxbd e16qazw91">图片：盖蒂图片社</span></figcaption></figure></section><p data-caps="initial" class="article__body-text article__body-text--dropcap"> <span data-caps="initial">8</span><small>月 15 日</small>，越南电动汽车 ( <small>EV</small> ) 制造商 VinFast 在美国纳斯达克证券交易所首次上市。这是一个相当不错的入口：公司股价飙升，市值从 230 亿美元飙升至 850 亿美元。这几乎相当于美国两大汽车制造商福特和通用汽车的总和，是其母公司 Vingroup 的七倍。 8 月 16 日，该数字略有下降，至 690 亿美元。 </p><style data-emotion="css 1lm38nn">.css-1lm38nn{margin:1.3125rem 0 2.1875rem;}.css-1lm38nn figure{margin:0;min-width:100%;}.css-1lm38nn figure figcaption{display:inline;font-family:var(--ds-type-system-sans);font-size:var(--ds-type-scale-0);font-weight:500;}.css-1lm38nn audio{display:block;margin-top:0.75rem;width:100%;}.css-1lm38nn +figure,.css-1lm38nn +.g-fallback+figure{margin-top:0;}</style><div class="css-1lm38nn e1lug06p0"><figure><div><figcaption>听听这个故事。 </figcaption><style data-emotion="css 1fs0t47">.css-1fs0t47{display:inline;font-family:var(--ds-type-system-sans);font-size:var(--ds-type-scale-0);font-style:normal;font-weight:400;line-height:var(--ds-type-leading-border-link);}.css-1fs0t47 a{color:var(--ds-color-london-5);-webkit-text-decoration:underline;text-decoration:underline;text-underline-offset:0.125rem;-webkit-transition:color var(--ds-interactions-transition),color var(--ds-interactions-transition);transition:color var(--ds-interactions-transition),color var(--ds-interactions-transition);}.css-1fs0t47 a:hover{color:var(--ds-color-chicago-30);}.css-1fs0t47 a:focus{text-decoration-color:transparent;box-shadow:0 0 0 0.125rem var(--ds-color-hong-kong-55);outline:solid transparent;}.css-1fs0t47 a:active{text-decoration-color:var(--ds-color-hong-kong-55);box-shadow:none;color:var(--ds-color-london-5);}</style><span class="css-1fs0t47 emsvzne0">在<a id="audio-ios-cta" href="https://economist-app.onelink.me/d2eC/bed1b25" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">iOS</a>或<a id="audio-android-cta" href="https://economist-app.onelink.me/d2eC/7f3c199" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Android</a>上享受更多音频和播客。</span> </div><audio class="react-audio-player " controls="" id="audio-player" preload="none" src="https://www.economist.com/media-assets/audio/062%20Business%20-%20Electric%20vehicles-bbbf7281ccbfd076244809cedd67fc7c.mp3" title="越南的电动汽车宠儿是否正在走向崩溃？" controlslist="nodownload"><p>您的浏览器不支持 &lt;audio>; 元素。 </p></audio><style data-emotion="css 1h1me4y">.css-1h1me4y{text-align:center;height:0;}.css-1h1me4y>div{top:-0.625rem;}</style><div class="css-1h1me4y e1lug06p1"><style data-emotion="css vu6x35">.css-vu6x35{position:relative;display:inline-block;text-align:left;}</style><div class="css-vu6x35 e5tfikp0"></div></div></figure></div><p class="article__body-text">投资者竞相入股 VinFast。该公司在<small>电动汽车</small>行业仍然是小鱼，但雄心勃勃。 5 月，该公司创始人、越南首富范一王 (Pham Nhat Vuong) 表示，公司希望今年销售 50,000 辆汽车，高于去年的 7,400 辆。尽管目前其大部分车辆在越南销售，但它也将目光投向了美国市场。上个月，该公司在北卡罗来纳州的一家工厂破土动工，并已开始在加利福尼亚州销售进口汽车，该公司在该州拥有 13 家经销店。</p><p class="article__body-text">评论并不热烈。行业记者凯文·威廉姆斯 (Kevin Williams) 表示，VinFast 在加利福尼亚州销售的<small>VF</small> 8 型号“根本没有准备好销往美国”。另一位评论家史蒂文·尤因（Steven Ewing）对这辆车的评价是“哎呀”，理由是转向体验很差。它的售价为 46,000 美元，与美国<small>电动汽车巨头</small>特斯拉等竞争对手提供的入门级车型相比，即使有的话，也便宜不了多少。据数据分析公司 Experian 称，2 月至 5 月期间，美国仅售出 128 辆<small>VF</small> 8。 </p><div class="adComponent_advert__V79Pp adComponent_incontent__Bxd2J adComponent_hidden___o_ZB advert--inline"><div><div id="econ-1" class="adComponent_adcontainer__dO1Zm"></div></div></div><p class="article__body-text">即使 VinFast 实现了今年的崇高增长目标，其估值仍将继续令人们信心不足。该公司去年净亏损 21 亿美元，并表示最早将于明年底实现收支平衡。咨询公司 AlixPartners 估计，<small>电动汽车</small>制造商每年需要生产约 40 万辆汽车才能开始盈利。此后，该公司距离赶上行业领先者还有很长的路要走。去年，特斯拉售出了 130 万辆<small>电动</small>汽车。快速增长的中国汽车制造商<small>比亚迪</small>售出了 190 万辆汽车，其中一半是纯电动车，一半是插电式混合动力车。</p><p class="article__body-text"> VinFast 仅有 1% 的股票进行交易，其高昂的市场估值很容易受到快速波动的影响。该公司的投资者可能会经历一段坎坷的旅程。 <span data-ornament="ufinish">■</span></p><p class="article__body-text"><i>要掌握商业和技术领域最重大的新闻，请订阅我们的每周订阅者<a href="https://www.economist.com/newsletters/the-bottom-line">简讯“底线”</a> 。</i></p> ]]>;</description><pubDate> Thu, 17 Aug 2023 10:01:31 GMT</pubDate><guid ispermalink="false"> /内容/pril296bhsd4s0db4ce4cu4ah8039hhj</guid><link/> https://www.economist.com/business/2023/08/17/is-vietnams-ev-darling-heading-for-a-crash </item><item><title><![CDATA[The battle between American workers and technology heats up]]></title><description><![CDATA[<section class="css-1ugvd2u e1y6i3a60"><style data-emotion="css j1vyw6">.css-j1vyw6 img{display:block;}.css-j1vyw6 .e16qazw92{margin-top:0.25rem;}</style><figure class="css-j1vyw6 e12yhaj20"><img alt="戴着工作手套的拳头粉碎了机器人手" fetchpriority="high" width="1280" height="720" decoding="async" data-nimg="1" style="color:transparent" sizes="(min-width: 960px) 700px, 95vw" srcset="https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=360,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230819_WBD000.jpg 360w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=384,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230819_WBD000.jpg 384w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=480,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230819_WBD000.jpg 480w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=600,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230819_WBD000.jpg 600w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=834,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230819_WBD000.jpg 834w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=960,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230819_WBD000.jpg 960w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=1096,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230819_WBD000.jpg 1096w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=1280,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230819_WBD000.jpg 1280w, https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=1424,quality=80,format=auto/content-assets/images/20230819_WBD000.jpg 1424w" src="https://www.economist.com/cdn-cgi/image/width=1424,quality=80,forma